{
  "stem": "7414.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was a very-- thing-- a thing which was very Przemysl because it was the first and only Jewish member of parliament from Przemysl, Lieberman, which was-- he was socially-- socialist.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So all the Jews voted, not because he was socialist or not, but because he was the first member of parliament, Jewish parliament.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were called the [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Lieberman ?] People.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But as I told you, we were very Jewish and Zionist oriented, the whole family, always.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father liked all the things which were new.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He did not have any formal education, not in those times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he was intelligent enough to be interested in, for example, from one-- once from a travel, he brought a beautiful encyclopedia, German encyclopedia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Or he was bringing books on when was-- in our time come to Jewish theater from Wilno.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was then a young girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He took me to see-- and I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I saw And I did not understand Yiddish, but I will still-- I still see Ida Kaminska on-- on the stage.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't play the piano.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not touch it from the day that the Russian came and took away my pianos and all my sheet music.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in 1939, and of course, with everything what we went through, that was the last on my mind too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was quite good at it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At 14, my teacher told my father that she can't-- they can't give me anymore in Przemysl-- that was quite a small town-- that he should send me to the conservatorium of music to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, it was quite time ago, and my father told, you don't send a child to a big town alone.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
